724467f-a.title: Manhattan: West End Avenue - 92nd Street (West)
724467f-a.text:
West End Avenue, west side, from 93rd to 92nd Streets, showing new
g75 West End Avenue, a 15-story apartment building rising on the
site of old 667-75, five-stony private houses. No. 677, adjoining
it on the north, is pictured in more detail in a 1912 photograph.
1923.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.

724466f-a.title: Manhattan: West End Avenue - 92nd Street (West)
724466f-a.text:
g77 West End Avenue, west side, between 92nd and 93rd Streets, a
private house built in the mid 1890's. The adjoining house, No.
675, will give way to a modern apartment building in 1923. See
view of the whole block in that year.
About 1912.
